messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Hello, somebody is coming into my house.
What's your address?
I can't hear you clearly, could you repeat your address?
5908, 722 and they have a gun.
5908. Is that 70 and 2nd Street?
Let me out. Let me out.
Stay on the line with me. What's going on?
I don't know. Get out of my house. Get out.
You stay in your house, ma'am.
I don't know. They have a gun. Get away from me.
Let me. Get away. Get away.
All right, ma'am, did you say 5908 70th and 2nd Street?
Listen to me. I need to know your address.
Do you take 70 seconds?
How many subjects are in the house?
Get out.
How many subjects are in the house?
Missing.
Ma'am, I cannot understand you. Please take a deep breath for me.
I can't.
How many subjects are in the house? Are you saying there's two people in the house?
I can't. I can't.
Please take a deep breath so I can understand you.
I can't. I can't.
What's going on?
I don't know. I think someone broke into my house.
Someone broke into your house?
I don't know. It was probably with the garage.
